"Rick's Touch Type Bindings. The default bindings are sadly one step to the
"left from the home row. The reason for this is probably that ';' is usually
"different letters in different languages.

"Map move cursor
map j <LEFT>
map k <DOWN>
map l <UP>
map ; <RIGHT>

"Map move windows
map <C-W>j <C-W><LEFT>
map <C-W>k <C-W><DOWN>
map <C-W>l <C-W><UP>
map <C-W>; <C-W><RIGHT>
